from the Licensor. Reinstatement is not automatic for repeated breaches.

11.5 On termination or expiration, You must immediately stop all unlicensed
use and delete or destroy all copies and modifications under Your control,
except archival copies required by law and published research materials that
do not contain the Software. Sections 5 through 16 survive termination to the
extent necessary to give them effect.

